metadata.name: Doodle #1
metadata.description: **Visit https://doodlesnft.shop for early access to artfully pixelated Doodles collection.**  Doodles have quickly become one of the most actively traded and highly valued NFT collections on OpenSea.  These 10,000 whimsical pieces of art have been carefully AI-pixelated.  Doodles is a community-driven project, an each NFT is made up of over a hundred traits.  In this public offering, only one minting is available for each of the 10,000 Doodles, and each owner will receive an individual ERC-721 token with proof of ownership on the Ethereum blockchain.
